FBIS3-30244 "dreeu021_d_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-021 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Feb 1994 SLOVAKIA Daily Corrects Commentary on Ethnic Hungarians AU3101125394 Bratislava REPUBLIKA in Slovak 28 Jan 93 p 2 AU3101125394 Bratislava REPUBLIKA Language: Slovak Article Type:BFN [Article by "r": "Correction"] [Text] In the article "Miklos Duray and Bela Bugar Keep Writing....," published in yesterday's issue of REPUBLIKA (pages 1 and 2), it should have been correctly stated that, in their letter addressed to the Council of Europe, Miklos Duray and Bela Bugar demand that "towns be given their historical Hungarian names" and not that "Hungarian towns be given their historical names," as incorrectly stated.
